######## BENCE   ######
#######################

IMAPAccount bence
Host mail.ferdinandy.com
User bence@ferdinandy.com
AuthMechs LOGIN
PassCmd "pass show aerc/bence | head -n1"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore bence-remote
Account bence

MaildirStore bence-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/.mail/bence/
Inbox ~/.mail/bence/Inbox

Channel bence-folders
Far :bence-remote:
Near :bence-local:
Patterns * !INBOX

Channel bence-inbox
Far ":bence-remote:INBOX"
Near ":bence-local:Inbox"

Group bence
Channel bence-inbox
Channel bence-folders

Group bence-fast
Channel bence-inbox
Channel bence-folders

